txt.en: The crate of Ranger supplies can be found in Echad Taerdim.\n\nYou should collect the supplies to take to the Rangers in Cirith Ungol.
'Thank you, friend. I was growing quite famished, and have not been able to find anything edible in these wilds. The plants and animals are all tainted!'
